OL,3,CMan's body recovered from river after
OL,4,Creports he got into difficulty
OL,6,FA 22-year-old man's body has been
OL,7,Frecovered from a river after it was
OL,8,Freported he got into difficulty during
OL,9,Fthe heatwave, police said.
OL,11,FBrody Leach's body was recovered from
OL,12,Fthe River Severn in Shrewsbury,
OL,13,FShropshire, on Saturday morning, West
OL,14,FMercia Police said.
OL,16,FThe area around the riverside where
OL,17,Fsearches were taking place has
OL,18,Freopened following searches for Mr
OL,19,FLeach after he entered the river on
OL,20,FFriday and then got into difficulty.
