OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782751678
OL,3,CMan's body recovered from river after
OL,4,Creports he got into difficulty
OL,6,FHe is the third person to have died in
OL,7,Fwater during this latest heatwave.
OL,9,FDuring the May heatwave, at least 15
OL,10,Fpeople, the majority of whom were
OL,11,Fchildren, drowned whilst swimming in
OL,12,Fopen water.
OL,14,FIt prompted widespread warnings about
OL,15,Fthe dangers of swimming in open water,
OL,16,Fwhich is often much colder than
OL,17,Fexpected and can cause cold water
OL,18,Fshock syndrome that can prove fatal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
