OL,3,CMan's body recovered from river after
OL,4,Creports he got into difficulty
OL,6,FWednesday was the first of three
OL,7,Fconsecutive days in which the hottest
OL,8,FJune day on record was broken.
OL,10,FFriday was confirmed by the Met Office
OL,11,Fas the UK's hottest June day on
OL,12,Frecord, with a provisional temperature
OL,13,Fof 37.3C recorded, surpassing the high
OL,14,Fof 36.7C.
